trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Net.WebClient.UploadProgressChanged" /> event of a <see cref="T:System.Net.WebClient" />.
Instances of this class are passed to the <xref:System.Net.UploadProgressChangedEventHandler>.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스의 인스턴스는에 전달 되는 <xref:System.Net.UploadProgressChangedEventHandler>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of bytes received.
An <see cref="T:System.Int64" /> value that indicates the number of bytes received.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Int64" /> 받은 바이트 수를 나타내는 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Uploading data to a server may result in a download from the server.
trans-unit.target: 서버에 데이터를 업로드 하는 중 서버에서 다운로드 하 여 발생할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: For example, suppose your application uploads a POST request to a Web server.
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어, 응용 프로그램 웹 서버에 POST 요청을 업로드 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The resulting download will update <xref:System.Net.UploadProgressChangedEventArgs.BytesReceived%2A> and <xref:System.Net.UploadProgressChangedEventArgs.TotalBytesToReceive%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 다운로드가 발생 하 여 업데이트 됩니다 <xref:System.Net.UploadProgressChangedEventArgs.BytesReceived%2A> 및 <xref:System.Net.UploadProgressChangedEventArgs.TotalBytesToReceive%2A>합니다.

trans-unit.source: To determine what percentage of the transfer has occurred, use the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ProgressChangedEventArgs.ProgressPercentage%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 전송의 비율 되었음을 확인 하려면는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.ProgressChangedEventArgs.ProgressPercentage%2A> 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: When the upload is complete, <xref:System.ComponentModel.ProgressChangedEventArgs.ProgressPercentage%2A> will be 50%.
trans-unit.target: 업로드가 완료 되 면 <xref:System.ComponentModel.ProgressChangedEventArgs.ProgressPercentage%2A> 50% 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: When the download completes, <xref:System.ComponentModel.ProgressChangedEventArgs.ProgressPercentage%2A> will be 100%.
trans-unit.target: 다운로드가 완료 되 면 <xref:System.ComponentModel.ProgressChangedEventArgs.ProgressPercentage%2A> 100% 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of bytes sent.
An <see cref="T:System.Int64" /> value that indicates the number of bytes sent.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Int64" /> 보낸 바이트 수를 나타내는 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the total number of bytes in a <see cref="T:System.Net.WebClient" /> data upload operation.
An <see cref="T:System.Int64" /> value that indicates the number of bytes that will be received.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Int64" /> 수신 될 바이트 수를 나타내는 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: To determine the number of bytes already received, use the <xref:System.Net.DownloadProgressChangedEventArgs.BytesReceived%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 이미 받은 바이트 수를 확인 하려면 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Net.DownloadProgressChangedEventArgs.BytesReceived%2A> 속성입니다.
